flowchart TD
    A[Author Submit] --> B[ME Technical Check]
    B -->|不通过| B1[Return to Author]
    B -->|通过| C[ME Assign AE]
    C --> D[AE Manage Reviewers]
    D --> D1[Selected: 内部 shortlist]
    D1 --> E[Send Invitation Email]
    E --> F{Reviewer Response}
    F -->|Decline| F1[Declined]
    F -->|Accept| G[Reviewer Workspace]
    G --> H[Reviewer Submit Report]
    H --> I{AE 是否已有足够证据?}
    I -->|否| D
    I -->|是| J[Exit Review Stage]
    J --> J1[Auto cancel selected / invited / opened]
    J --> J2[AE 显式处理 accepted but not submitted]
    J1 --> K{下一步路径}
    J2 --> K
    K -->|直接给 revision 建议| L[Decision / Revision]
    K -->|送 First Decision| M[Academic / EIC Decision]
    K -->|证据非常明确| N[Final Decision]
    M --> O[Major Revision / Minor Revision / Reject]
    N --> P[Accept / Reject / Revision]
    P --> Q[Production + Finance]
    Q --> R[Publish]

